Subtitle\
--------\
A week of quiet consolidation as media, civil service, and immigration enforcement are reshaped to serve executive power while courts and civil society fight rearguard actions.\
\
Tagline / Hook\
-------------\
The clock does not move, yet the circuitry beneath it is rewired to favor power over scrutiny, loyalty over law, and narrative over fact.\
